    openedCardTitle: ACHILLES
    openedCardTitleKey: ACHILLES
    openedCardFrontDescription: "<b>Character:</b> Achilles\n<b>Represents:</b> Homo
      sapiens\n<b>Era:</b> Ancient Greece / Spartan era\n<b>Time:</b> about 2500
      years ago\n<b>Status:</b> Living species\n<b>Size:</b> around 1.7 meters tall\n\n<b>Focus:</b>
      \nHuman bone structures, archaeology, and cultural meaning."
    openedCardFrontDescriptionKey: REWARD_ACHILLES_FRONT
    openedCardBackDescription: In this mission, you decoded bone amulets by observing
      their shape and meaning. In archaeology, bones can become objects of memory,
      identity, belief, and culture.
    openedCardBackDescriptionKey: REWARD_ACHILLES_BACK
